title: Watch: Meet NCT 127’s Newest Member Johnny In Comeback Teasers
text:
NCT 127 has revealed the latest individual teasers for their upcoming comeback! 
This time it’s Johnny’s turn. Johnny is the newest addition to NCT and will be debuting through NCT 127. He was previously a part of SM Rookies and has been training with SM Entertainment since 2008 or so. The Korean-American hails from Chicago. Meet him in his teasers below! 
NCT 127 will release their second mini album “LIMITLESS” on January 9. 
Stay tuned for updates!
